OL,3,CSafeguarding and costs concerns for
OL,4,Cnext year's Island Games
OL,6,FEvery two years over 3,000 athletes
OL,7,Ffrom islands around the globe,
OL,8,Fincluding teams from the Channel
OL,9,FIslands come together to compete at
OL,10,Fthe Island Games.
OL,12,FBut, there have been increasing
OL,13,Fconcerns about Orkney's ability to
OL,14,Fhost next year's event.
OL,16,FIt is the smallest nation ever to host
OL,17,Fthe games with a population of just
OL,18,F21,500.
