OL,3,CSafeguarding and costs concerns for
OL,4,Cnext year's Island Games
OL,6,FHousing the thousands of athletes
OL,7,Facross such a small set of islands
OL,8,Fwill be an issue.
OL,10,FKirsty Talbot Director, Orkney Island
OL,11,FGames 2025 said: "We have a few hotels
OL,12,Fbut they're not very big, so we've had
OL,13,Fto look at the dormitory side of
OL,14,Fthings."
OL,16,FOver 700 athletes will be housed in
OL,17,Fdormitories in schools and many others
OL,18,Fwill be housed in hostels, host
OL,19,Fresidences and 'containerized
OL,20,Faccommodation' is also being
OL,21,Fconsidered.
