OL,3,CSafeguarding and costs concerns for
OL,4,Cnext year's Island Games
OL,6,FSome teams, including Alderney, have
OL,7,Falready cut the size of their team
OL,8,Fbecause of the high cost and
OL,9,Fchallenging logistics around
OL,10,Ftravelling to such a remote
OL,11,Fdestination.
OL,13,FIt costs around #2000 per competitor
OL,14,Fto take part, even winners from the
OL,15,Flast games held in Guernsey in 2023
OL,16,Fare having their doubts.
OL,18,FJersey archer, Lucy O'Sullivan said:
OL,19,F"Obviously, I won five gold medals in
OL,20,FGuernsey, so I'd love to be able to
OL,21,Fcompete at the next one.
